    "title": "[hd256] Improve forward kernel with exp2 FMA emulation (3% to 9% performance gain)",
    "user": {
      "login": "Johnsonms",
      "id": 8664132,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg2NjQxMzI=",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8664132?v=4",
